tool_description: Real Love Calculator is a love calculator which uses male and female names and their date of birth to determine the love compatibility. It is completely based on astrological calculations and thus gives real prediction compatibility score.
title: Real Love Calculator

api_list.name: GET /
api_list.description: It is use to check if this API is working. Make sure that you use POST API and not the GET API.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://real-love-calculator.p.rapidapi.com/"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "real-love-calculator.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
